===Interjection===
'''bother!'''

# A mild expression of annoyance.
'''1926''' "Oh, help!" said Pooh. "I'd better go back."
:"Oh, '''bother'''!" said Pooh. "I shall have to go on."
:"I can't do either!" said Pooh. "Oh, help and '''bother'''!"
:''Winnie the Pooh A A Milne. Methuen & Co., Ltd., 1926 Chapter 2 ...in which Pooh goes visiting and gets into a tight place''
